            <h1>SMG Pubs / Ranked</h1>
            <img src="ksv loadout.png" alt = "KSV photo" height = "300" width = "400">
            <p>- This loadout is for the smg players in pubs who like to run around the map and get quick kills.</p>
            <p>KSV: Ported Compensator, Long Barrel, Ranger Foregrip, Extended Mag I, and Recoil Springs.</p>
            <p>Greykova: Long Barrel, Extended Mag III, HipFire Laser, Akimbo, FMJ Rounds.</p>
            <p>Melee: Knife</p>
            <p>Perks: Gung Ho, Assassin, Double Time, and Flak Jacket.</p>
            <p>Tactical: Stim Shot.</p>
            <p>Lethal: Semtex.</p>
            <p>Field Upgrade: Assault Pack or Trophy System.</p>
            <p>Wildcard: Perk Greed</p>
            <img src="jackal loadout.png" alt = "Jackal photo" height = "300" width = "400">
            <p>- This loadout is for ranked to help you stay on the objective.</p>
            <p>Jackal: Ported Compensator, Reinforced Barrel, Ranger Foregrip, CQB Grip, and Recoil Springs.</p>
            <p>Stryder .22: Kepler Microflex, Fast Mag II, and Quickdraw Grip.</p>
            <p>Melee: Knife</p>
            <p>Perks: Flak Jacket, Fast Hands, Double Time, and Ninja.</p>
